          <h2>Single-Zone vs. Multi-Zone Systems</h2>
          <p><strong>Single-Zone:</strong> One outdoor unit connects to one indoor unit. Ideal for cooling a single room or space.</p>
          <p><strong>Multi-Zone:</strong> One outdoor unit connects to multiple indoor units (up to 8). Each zone has independent temperature control. Perfect for whole-home comfort or multiple rooms.</p>

